parameters:
Orca Mayor: Damn it... damn it all...!! If only I had
money... those days could have lasted forever...! Damn it
all!!!

Memimi: You should have tried again and again, Orca Mayor...
You're a weakling who ran to money after a single failure
broke your spirit! No matter how many times I lose, I'll
keep fighting until I win. There's no way I'll ever submit
to the likes of you!!!

Orca Mayor: Shut up!! Damn it... this is my last resort!
With Orca Doping, I'll gain overwhelming power and knock you
down!!

Orca Mayor: Oooh... I can feel the power surging...! Right
now, I've obtained the ultimate power and endurance... It's
the final showdown, you little girl...!!

Memimi: Then, I too shall resort to my final measure... The
monster who was defeated and became your pawn, Dynamite
Abalone... His power has also become part of my flesh and
blood, just like the other monsters in the city.

Memimi: Behold, the Abalone Dynamite bestowed upon me by the
great leader himself!!! This is my... final power!!!

Bunny-chan: Congratulations~♪ Victory goes to Shark Duke-
san!!! Hooray!
Memimi has finally defeated the Orca Mayor...!

Orca Mayor: Damn it... damn it all...!! If only I had
money... those days could have lasted forever...! Damn it
all!!!

Memimi: You should have tried again and again, Orca Mayor...
You're a weakling who ran to money after a single failure!
I, who will fight until I win no matter how many times I
lose, will never bow to you!!!

Orca Mayor: Shut up!! Damn it... is there nothing left...?
Anyone, I don't care who, cover me-!!!

Dynamite Abalone: Aba... Aba... Huff huff... I've finally
made it... There's still damage left, but I had to make it
here...!

Orca Mayor: Dynamite Abalone...! You came for me!!
Shashasha~, this is a turnaround, isn't it!?

Anomalocaris Mosman: Gahhh, that Dynamite Abalone guy, he's
come back to life!! This is bad... even if he's injured, we
might not be able to handle that monster with all of us...

Bunny-chan: Get out of the way-! Why now of all times...
What should we do...

Shark Broccoli: No, wait... everyone, there's no need to
worry...

Dynamite Abalone: Orca Duke... I'm sorry, it was my
fault...! Seeing you never give up no matter how much you're
beaten, I've come to my senses... Use my monster parts
too...!

Memimi: This is the end, Orca Mayor!! The crystallization of
the power of the strongest monsters in the city! Take this
full-powered... Abalone Dynamite!!!

Bunny-chan: Congratulations~♪ Victory goes to Orca
Duke---!!! Hooray!
Memimi has finally defeated the Orca Mayor...!
